OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FSo what could the future hold for this
OL,7,Fsteelworks and the surrounding
OL,8,Fcommunities?
OL,10,FPart of that future will be built on
OL,11,Fthe #1.25 billion investment by Tata
OL,12,Fand the UK Government in a new
OL,13,Felectric arc furnace. Plans are
OL,14,Falready underway to build what Tata
OL,15,Fdescribes as a green steel plant which
OL,16,Fwill secure steelmaking on site for
OL,17,Ffuture generations.
