OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FIts success, in terms of both
OL,7,Fprofitability and lowering carbon,
OL,8,Fwill depend on electricity. The ideal
OL,9,Fsituation would be to use low-carbon
OL,10,Felectricity from floating offshore
OL,11,Fwind farms or eventually from
OL,12,Fhydrogen, but that technology and
OL,13,Finfrastructure is not in place yet.
OL,15,FIn the shorter term, steel will be
OL,16,Fimported into Port Talbot for
OL,17,Fdownstream processing until the
OL,18,Felectric arc furnace is built. Steel
OL,19,Funions have argued this not only
OL,20,Fincreases the carbon footprint of the
OL,21,Fsteel but it also exports Welsh jobs.
