OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FThe unions had argued for a slower
OL,7,Ftransition to the blast furnaces being
OL,8,Fshut down so people would have a
OL,9,Fchance to retrain and regroup, but
OL,10,FTata insists it is the only way to
OL,11,Fsecure steelmaking in Port Talbot for
OL,12,Fthe future.
