OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FThe hope is that offshore floating
OL,7,Fwind production in the Celtic Sea
OL,8,Fcould provide the anchor for future
OL,9,Fjobs and prosperity here. There are
OL,10,Fplans for this low-carbon energy
OL,11,Fproduction to be centred around the
OL,12,Fports of Milford Haven and Port Talbot
OL,13,Fwhich form the Celtic Free Ports.
OL,14,FOffshore wind needs infrastructure,
OL,15,Fsteel and services.
