OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FThe challenge is to produce and
OL,7,Fmanufacture as many of those products
OL,8,Fhere in Wales to gain the maximum
OL,9,Feconomic benefit locally, creating
OL,10,Fjobs and prosperity. It's a huge task
OL,11,Ffor the supply chain in terms of time
OL,12,Fand capacity, to be ready to make the
OL,13,Fmost of these new opportunities.
OL,15,FNet Zero Industry Wales, the body
OL,16,Fspearheading Wales' shift to a lower-
OL,17,Fcarbon future, says both governments
OL,18,Fneed to work together at pace so these
OL,19,Fonce-in-a-lifetime opportunities are
OL,20,Fnot lost.
