OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FCheaper, greener power will attract
OL,7,Finvestment and other companies to the
OL,8,Fregion. However, Wales is operating in
OL,9,Fa global marketplace, and as Port
OL,10,FTalbot steel has been exported around
OL,11,Fthe world for decades, this region
OL,12,Fwill need to act quickly to beat off
OL,13,Fother areas looking to transform their
OL,14,Fown economies.
