OL,3,CPort Talbot's blast furnaces now
OL,4,Cbelong to history but what's next?
OL,6,FPort Talbot is not alone. Other areas
OL,7,Flike Teeside, where steel has also
OL,8,Fformed the bedrock of the regional
OL,9,Feconomy for decades, are having to
OL,10,Fchange too. Like Tata, British Steel
OL,11,Fis closing its blast furnaces at
OL,12,FScunthorpe.
OL,14,FHowever there is hope, opportunity and
OL,15,Foptimism for the next chapter.
OL,16,FElectric arc furnaces are the future
OL,17,Fbut getting there is a long, painful
OL,18,Froad for those people and communities
OL,19,Flosing livelihoods today.
